The paper deals with reactive synthesis, which is a topic in formal methods and logic. The use of automata and transducers suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-categories of Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO) or Formal Languages and Automata Theory (cs.FL). The use of registers and the study of bounded synthesis suggest that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of Programming Languages (cs.PL) or Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS). Finally, the study of infinite words suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-category of Computation and Language (cs.CL).
